Hosted by Patty Carluccio and Stacy Kershaw, Pretty. Simple. Gardens. shows you simple ways to make your garden look pretty!

Patty and Stacy are both amateur gardeners who love spending time making their gardens look beautiful without a lot of fuss. They offer down to earth advice and show you tried and tested techniques that can help your garden thrive.

Episode 1 - Pretty Pots: This episode will show you how to easily fill a pretty pot for fall.